snippet.title: Best VGM 1700 - Mario Kart 8 - Toad Harbor / Toad's Turnpike
snippet.description:
See also:
Best VGM 1565 - https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=dhGMZwQr0Iw
Best VGM 1724 - http://youtu.be/jlcjrgSVkkc
Best VGM 2363 - https://youtu.be/0tZ8axZV3QA

A collection of my favorite videogame music. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

Wii U
Mario Kart 8 (2014)
Toad Harbor / Toad's Turnpike
Asuka Ota & Ryo Nagamatsu
